70.greeting:
{Death Chamber}

As you approach the ominous skull structure, you are greeted by a grotesque Undead King. "You have found one of my Death Chambers", the king says in a sinister voice. "I assume you are here to try to steal my ancient treasures? If you enter this chamber, I will punish you with the deadliest force imaginable.

Will you heed my warning or suffer a treacherous death?"

